  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the grill to a medium-high heat</p>\r\n<p>Cut the<strong> yellow pepper<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> in half (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon)</p>\r\n<p>Add the <strong>yellow pepper<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> to a baking tray, skin-side up, and place them directly under the grill for 8-10 min or until the <strong>pepper<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> has blackened slightly (charring adds a smoky flavour!)</p>\r\n<p>Once cooked, set aside to cool slightly</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1030.-step-1-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1030.-step-1-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1030.-step-1-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1030.-step-1-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1030.-step-1-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine the <strong>lamb&nbsp;mince</strong> with the<strong> panko breadcrumbs</strong>, <strong>smoked paprika</strong> and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p>\r\n<p>Mix thoroughly (clean hands are best!), then divide the mixture into 8 <span class=\"text-danger\">[16]</span> pieces</p>\r\n<p>Shape into <strong>meatballs</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1030.-step-2-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1030.-step-2-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1030.-step-2-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1030.-step-2-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1030.-step-2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a medium-high heat with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p>\r\n<p>Once hot, add the <strong>meatballs</strong> and cook for 2-3 min on each side or until browned&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Tip:&nbsp;over-crowding the pan can make the meatballs sweat, so cook them in batches if needed</p>\r\n<p>Once browned, transfer the&nbsp;<strong>meatballs&nbsp;</strong>to a plate and keep the pan for later</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1030.-step-3-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1030.-step-3-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1030.-step-3-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1030.-step-3-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1030.-step-3-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel and finely dice the <strong>red onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p>\r\n<p>Chop the <strong>courgette<span class=\"text-danger\"><strong>[s]</strong></span></strong> into small pieces</p>\r\n<p>Once cooled, cut the charred <strong>yellow pepper<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> into strips</p>\r\n<p>Boil a kettle</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1030.-step-4-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1030.-step-4-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
